{"tid":985369,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"內地《鹹蛋支人》拍續集 日方指侵權告到底","createTime":"2019-01-17T13:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T13:53:21.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f991d34033288a95a0853411143b1c007fc4a5a7","tid":985369,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"【涉未經授權】內地《鹹蛋超人》拍續集 日方指侵權告到底<br />\n「內地版」鹹蛋超人電影《鋼鐵飛龍之再見奧特曼》2017年上映時，被擁有鹹蛋超人版權嘅圓谷製作公司稱侵權提告，點知官司都未打完，《鋼鐵飛龍》續集《鋼鐵飛龍之奧特曼崛起》已製作完成，並安排聽日於內地上映。<br />\n《鋼鐵飛龍之奧特曼崛起》繼續由廣州藍弧動畫製作，故仔講「奧特曼」即係鹹蛋超人，揀咗一個平凡男孩做伴一齊拯救地球。去年內地製作方堅稱自己係攞正牌拍攝，反而日方就指佢哋侵權，而於日方再三警告下，內地公司一於少理繼續拍續集。<br />\n日本近日都有就「內地版」鹹蛋超人上映作報道，佢哋形容中國侵權文化已經唔係今日開始，一句話「冇侵權」就製作電影續編，一啲罪惡感都冇。圓谷方面就稱，被告方繼續製作鹹蛋超人電影及發行係侵權行為，將會採取相應法律行動。<br />\n<img src=\"http://s10.sinaimg.cn/middle/674f4736g9f5f6c9bdd39&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs10.sinaimg.cn%2Fmiddle%2F674f4736g9f5f6c9bdd39%26690&h=57638e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190117/59154020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F59154020&d=D1Y0%2Fdp%2BO8vcwf99EFFcLOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=b32096ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F59154020&h=e4ebbd8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190117/59154020</a>"},{"pid":"4dc5d9128d4018e1168646c02ca27d74afd17d94","tid":985369,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eeb830569500ddc5f7f8ff2c828e9791a48dc22","tid":985369,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"之前聽過背後原來有呢個故事,大家參考下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JFy3M4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\